al, Visual Question Answering (VQA), Visual\nEntailment and Visual Reasoning. Our approach not only outperforms the\nstate-of-the-art VLP performance, but also shows benefits on the IMF metric.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2021 08:04:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 04:42:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Nov 2021 15:25:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 9 Nov 2021 06:27:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-10"}
