s safety goals to threats and to\nattacks explicitly. Hence, the coverage of safety concerns by security testing\nis assured. Two use cases of vehicle communication and autonomous driving are\ninvestigated to prove the applicability of the approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jun 2021 08:36:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
